{"tid":1504002,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"建議9月尾周末18區遊行+人鏈","createTime":"2019-08-25T07:07:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-25T07:36:36.000Z","uid":175748,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"9fbf0992037df542efff8161dfad1ab087266e8e","tid":1504002,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:07:21.000Z","msg":"我先講以下建議係要大量組織呼籲同支持先做到，所以就提議係9月尾先搞。<br />\n係我地兩個月社運之後，我覺得搞18區和理非遊行都唔會話唔夠人。<br />\n<br />\n好處一；<span style=\"color: red;\">方便義工計算人數。</span><br />\n好處二；<span style=\"color: red;\">18區人數分散，中午遊行，黃昏前已經可以組織人鏈。</span><br />\n好處三；如果有民間團體支持，人鏈人數大增，<span style=\"color: red;\">亦唔需要擔心其他日子要承受不必要既風險。</span><br />\n<br />\n壞處一；如果無清晰既分工，分散18區人數會嚴重不足，如記者及主辦單位既義工<br />\n壞處二；分散各區難應付突發情況，如發生衝突，醫護、議員、記者未必能及時趕到幫忙<br />\n<br />\n我自己就18區遊行有幾個建議<br />\n一；<span style=\"color: red;\">相鄰既區域，設定遊行終點係兩區接近既地方，以便連接人鏈及作其他安排</span>，舉例：屯門元朗區一齊行近洪水橋方向；大埔北區就行近九龍坑方向。<br />\n二；18區遊行由不同單位主辦，例如民陣依舊負責港島區，其他民間組織安排人手新界及九龍區。"},{"pid":"d398a93674289967ce5fbf02b2741fe0680da3b6","tid":1504002,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:12:17.000Z","msg":"人鏈唔好不斷做，諗下新野"},{"pid":"1996c3bf388edf818e13d0dbb5d23a1678a370c8","tid":1504002,"uid":175748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:28:50.000Z","msg":"九月試多次<br />\n百萬人版<br />\n我覺得ok"},{"pid":"e8d6a776cc86e07f5e72b755298fca88754435b8","tid":1504002,"uid":29899,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:29:25.000Z","msg":"日期: 2019．9．1<br />\n時間: 13:00<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YyFriWu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYyFriWu.jpg&h=47e393ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q0mmSi0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ0mmSi0.jpg&h=e2509c0c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[9．1機場] 官逼民反，民不得不反<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dJNfyS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dJNfyS</a>"},{"pid":"9af0d863f76069e66470dd4a7b46f09b33e98635","tid":1504002,"uid":169079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:31:54.000Z","msg":"入機場"},{"pid":"b6d0da7385e4c43da95eb340d07a44f4bb1cca28","tid":1504002,"uid":95138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:33:35.000Z","msg":"又18區<br />\n機場又要排隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0028c9077e3fffdc497206521cd42bb3ec0c198","tid":1504002,"uid":21761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"唔建議再做人鏈 睇下九月歷史上有冇其他左膠和理非紀念活動仲好"},{"pid":"fd27ef874dafa0d27787e301ed4e01b8088c0821","tid":1504002,"uid":53612,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-25T07:36:36.000Z","msg":"要集中 機場活動"}]}